title: IAA Tonight | CMC to SF, Week 7 Picks, and the Start of #WembanyamaTankSZN
description: Christian McCaffrey is headed to San Francisco. Is he still the same impact player? Can he take the Niners to the top? And who's on the next flight out of Carolina? Plus, Omar Kelly, Brandon Flowers, Antoine Walker, and Leger Douzable make their Week 7 picks, and hit the start of the NBA season. Has the tanking for Victor Wembanyama ALREADY begun?
